all on its own. And he said, "Aha. There must

00:32:31.650 --> 00:32:36.830
be some low frequency sound that I can't hear."
And he got a hold of some sound testing equipment.

00:32:36.830 --> 00:32:44.210
And he found out that indeed, there was 19
Hertz at a pretty substantial amplitude.

00:32:44.210 --> 00:32:51.120
