in that lab, starting at five, ten, fifteen,

00:32:51.120 --> 00:32:56.870
twenty Hertz. You can see that giant peak
just at about 19 Hertz. He measured the room

00:32:56.870 --> 00:33:00.740
and found out that the room was exactly half
the length of a 19 Hertz wavelength, which

00:33:00.740 --> 00:33:10.170
is some 30, 33, 30 -something feet, I believe.
And the lab was half of that.

00:33:10.170 --> 00:33:12.679
