00:34:06.090 --> 00:34:10.760
the same place--almost 19 Hertz. And it turns
out that this approximately 19 Hertz -- it's

00:34:10.760 --> 00:34:15.539
gonna be a little bit different for everyone,
is the resonant frequency of your eyeball.

00:34:15.539 --> 00:34:16.940
And you can test that by if you--.

00:34:16.940 --> 00:34:21.049
You know, if you ping a wine glass, the note
